During the 3Q25, the company sold an investment, which led to nonrecurring JAM FINTOP partnership income.^Sch PIA, item 11: In the 3Q25, we paid a cash dividend of 0.15 per share. This was an increase from 0.12 in the prior two quarters.^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^WWW.REDRIVERBANK.NET^71301^^^^
